				<img src="../uploads/images/wp-2.jpg" alt="Wp 2" height="">
			</div>
			</div>
</div>
	<div class="container-max mx-auto copy__wrapper clearfix">
	<div class="lg:w-2/3 mx-auto">
		<p>All images except for last are sourced from the De Gournay website. </p>
	</div>
